k membuat pelet kayu berkinerja terbaik di seluruh dunia.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#f9f9f9\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_line_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.2,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9002612\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"46\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"32\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"739691c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"6b65a86\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"21\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"25\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"202abbc\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7ae9c35\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Indonesia is the highest biomass potential in South East Asia countries so that the chances of developing wood pellet industry is huge.<\\/p><p>Indonesia have many various types of pellets (wood pellet, torrefied wood pellet &amp; charcoal pellet) Biomass decomposition regimes[:id]Indonesia merupakan negara dengan potensi biomassa tertinggi di Asia Tenggara sehingga peluang pengembangan industri wood pellet yang sangat besar.<br \\/>Indonesia memiliki berbagai jenis pelet kayu, pelet kayu torrefied &amp; pelet arang[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#757575\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
