l lainnya.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"7700d95\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"height\":\"min-height\",\"custom_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":384,\"sizes\":[]},\"custom_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":392,\"sizes\":[]},\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Eco-Friendly-Indonesia-Wood-Pellet.jpeg\",\"id\":3668},\"background_position\":\"center center\",\"background_position_mobile\":\"center center\",\"background_xpos_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":113,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_ypos_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"vh\",\"size\":\"\",\"sizes\":[]},\"background_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_repeat_mobile\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_size\":\"contain\",\"background_size_mobile\":\"cover\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_effect\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_direction\":\"negative\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_speed\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"81f53ba\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"cdcb02e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"rgba(12,12,12,0.46)\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"38c27b9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Our stringent quality standards apply to every single pellet and exceeds industry standards. While a primary goal of our company has been to constantly improve and evolve our premium wood pellets, one thing has never changed: our dedication to make the best performing wood pellets around the world.[:id]Standar kualitas ketat kami lakukan untuk setiap pelet dalam standar industri. Tujuan utama perusahaan kami adalah untuk terus meningkatkan dan mengembangkan pelet kayu premium, dedikasi kami untuk membuat pelet kayu berkinerja terbaik di seluruh dunia.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#f9f9f9\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_line_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.2,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9002612\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"46\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"32\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"739691c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"6b65a86\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"21\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"25\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"202abbc\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7ae9c35\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Indonesia is the highest biomass potential in South East Asia countries so that the chances of developing wood pellet industry is huge.<\\/p><p>Indonesia have many various types of pellets (wood pellet, torrefied wood pellet &amp; charcoal pellet) Biomass decomposition regimes[:id]Indonesia merupakan negara dengan potensi biomassa tertinggi di Asia Tenggara sehingga peluang pengembangan industri wood pellet yang sangat besar.<br \\/>Indonesia memiliki berbagai jenis pelet kayu, pelet kayu torrefied &amp; pelet arang[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#757575\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
