(1169, 3685, '_madxartwork_data', '[{\"id\":\"63a1e3e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6bf09c0\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8c43237\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Add Your Heading Text Here\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#aaaaaa\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":23,\"sizes\":[]},\"__dynamic__\":{\"title\":\"[madxartwork-tag id=\\\"67d897a\\\" name=\\\"post-title\\\" settings=\\\"%7B%7D\\\"]\",\"link\":\"[madxartwork-tag id=\\\"545ae63\\\" name=\\\"post-url\\\" settings=\\\"%7B%7D\\\"]\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"17205c4\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4c12f0e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4f0d6a2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/livestock-using-wood-pellets.jpg\",\"id\":3709}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c9985ee\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"344531f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":31.256},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5163eea\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Albasia-Wood.jpg\",\"id\":3705},\"image_size\":\"medium_large\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8ea1d56\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":68.744},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7211f6c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Currently Falcataria moluccana \\/ Albasia wood became one of the raw materials in the manufactured of wood pellets, because F. moluccana has a fast growing properties. However F. moluccana pellets have a high ash content, and high S and N content, with low calorific value which could not meet requirement of EnPlus standard for pellet. To improve its properties, pellets were manufactured using mixtures of F. moluccana particles to coconut shell particles, and the properties were investigated. The objectives of this study were to determine effect of the combination material of F. moluccana with coconut shell on different particle size and different compressive force. A material was from F. moluccana sawdust waste and coconut shell waste (Cocos nucifera L.). [:id]Kayu sengon menjadi salah satu bahan baku dalam pembuatan pelet kayu karena memiliki sifat yang cepat tumbuh. Akan tetapi pelet kayu sengon memiliki kadar abu, kadar sulfur dan nitrogen yang tinggi serta nilai kalor yang rendah sehingga belum dapat memenuhi spesifikasi standar pelet kayu (EnPlus). Untuk meningkatkan sifat bahan bakar pelet kayu maka dilakukan pencampuran bahan dengan serbuk tempurung kelapa. Diketahui tempurung kelapa memiliki nilai kalor yang tinggi, dan kadar abu, sulfur dan nitrogen yang rendah. Penelitian ini bertujuan untuk mengetahui pengaruh kombinasi bahan sengon dengan tempurung kelapa pada ukuran partikel dan tekanan kempa yang berbeda. Penelitian ini menggunakan bahan dari limbah serbuk gergaji sengon (Falcataria moluccana (Miq.)) dan limbah tempurung kelapa (Cocos nucifera). [:]\",\"text_color\":\"#7f7f7f\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9f92353\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"height\":\"min-height\",\"custom_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":450,\"sizes\":[]},\"custom_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":450,\"sizes\":[]},\"marvy_firework_animation_color_multiples\":[{\"color\":\"#f51720\",\"_id\":\"d534a3a\"},{\"color\":\"#fa26a0\",\"_id\":\"476c0fa\"},{\"color\":\"#f8d210\",\"_id\":\"7be2fbd\"},{\"color\":\"#2ff3e0\",\"_id\":\"fec7218\"}],\"marvy_beyblade_animation_color_multiples\":[{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"166b572\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"e8be500\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"964bb2d\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"7324d01\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"7683152\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"8003910\"}],\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-Animal-Bedding-and-Litter.jpg\",\"id\":3606},\"background_position\":\"center right\",\"background_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_size\":\"cover\",\"box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"slider_delay\":\"5000\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_effect\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_direction\":\"negative\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_speed\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10,\"sizes\":[]},\"custom_height_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":450,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"eaf95ad\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":53.04,\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"rgba(12,12,12,0.35)\",\"slider_delay\":\"5000\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation\":\"fadeInUp\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation_duration\":\"fast\",\"margin_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":false},\"animation\":\"fadeInUp\",\"animation_duration\":\"fast\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"22e770a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]Wood Pellets for Cattle and Pets[:id]Wood Pellet untuk binatang[:]\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"title_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation\":\"fadeInRight\",\"_animation\":\"fadeInUp\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"70f8657\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Significant part to guarantee the live quality of the animals[:id]Bagian penting untuk menjamin kualitas hidup hewan[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#f2f2f2\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_line_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.4,\"sizes\":[]},\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation\":\"fadeInRight\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation_duration\":\"slow\",\"_animation\":\"fadeInUp\",\"animation_duration\":\"slow\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a875cdf\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":46.96,\"slider_delay\":\"5000\"},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"804d627\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d2890d2\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":57.718},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f692b6c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]In this study was applied Completely Randomized Design, treated by 3 factors, there were particle size (20-40; 40-60; and 60-80 mesh), various material combination of F. moluccana and coconut shell (100%:0%; 75%:25%; 50%:50%; and 25%:75%), and different compressive force (70 and 100 kg\\/cm2). Physical and chemical properties are investigated including compressive strength, hygroscopicity response, specific gravity, proximat analysis, ultimate analysis, and calorific value. The result showed that adding coconut shell particles to F. moluccana particles was an effective way to improve fuel properties of F. moluccana pellets. The best mixed pellets are produced when adding 50% coconut shell to F. moluccana, with particle size 60-80 mesh and press load of 100 kg\\/cm2 that produce mixed pellets with the following specifications: ash content 1.02%, nitrogen content 0.38%, sulfur content 0.05%, furthermore calorific value also improved 5177.04 cal\\/g. The result from this research already comply the grade requirement of EnPlus standard.[:id]Penelitian ini menggunakan rancangan acak lengkap (Completely Randomized Design) dengan 3 faktor perlakuan, yaitu ukuran partikel (20-40; 40-60; dan 60-80 mesh), persentase kombinasi bahan sengon dan tempurung kelapa (100:0%, 75:25%, 50:50%, dan 25:75%), dan tekanan kempa (70 dan 100 kg\\/m2). Parameter yang diamati antara lain sifat fisika (berat jenis, respon higroskopisitas, dan keteguhan tekan), sifat proksimat (kadar air, abu, zat terbang, dan karbon terikat), sifat ultimat (C, H, O, N, dan S), dan nilai kalor. Hasil penelitian menunjukkan kombinasi bahan baku yang berbeda (sengon dan tempurung kelapa) memberikan pengaruh terhadap sifat fisika dan kimia pelet kayu, kecuali pada kadar air. Ukuran partikel dan tekanan kempa berpengaruh nyata terhadap sifat fisika dan kimia pelet kayu kecuali pada kadar zat mudah meenguap, dan kadar abu. Pelet kayu terbaik dihasilkan pada kombinasi serbuk sengon dan tempurung kelapa 50%:50%, ukuran partikel 60-80 mesh, dan tekanan kempa 100 kg\\/cm2, menghasilkan pelet dengan kadar abu 1,02%, kadar N 0,38%, kadar S 0,05% dan nilai kalor 5177,04 kal\\/g. Hasil penelitian tersebut telah memenuhi standar EnPlus.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#6b6b6b\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a9ea66a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":42.282},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b5b6c12\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"gallery\":[{\"id\":3707,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Wood-pellet-cat-litter.jpg\"},{\"id\":3708,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Straw-Pellets.jpg\"},{\"id\":3586,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Wood-Pellet-for-animal-farm.jpg\"},{\"id\":3665,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-High-Quality-Wood-Pellet.jpg\"},{\"id\":3668,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Eco-Friendly-Indonesia-Wood-Pellet.jpeg\"}],\"galleries\":[{\"gallery_title\":\"New Gallery\",\"_id\":\"300b396\",\"multiple_gallery\":[]}],\"gallery_layout\":\"justified\",\"ideal_row_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":160,\"sizes\":[]},\"ideal_row_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":133,\"sizes\":[]},\"thumbnail_image_size\":\"medium_large\",\"show_all_galleries_label\":\"All\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"gallery\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d2b0709\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7a7fe7b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a0b9b01\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]Advantages of Albasia Woods[:id]Kelebihan Kayu Sengon[:]\",\"title_color\":\"#878787\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":25,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"971fde9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Wood Pellet This product is made from natural or organic wood without being mixed with chemicals so it is very safe for pets. Even if eaten, this wood pellet will be wasted through feces in a crushed form, not in its original form. Wood pellets are useful as a base\\/substrate in pet cages because they absorb pee and minimize the smell of feces. Some breeders also use wood pellets for new born \\/ hatched pets because the wood we use is made from natural materials so that animals will like their cages and not get stressed easily. High absorption and low \\/ economical price can replace zeolite sand which is commonly used for pet cages. The disposal can be directly thrown into the ground and will be destroyed with the ground. Unlike zeolite sand which is difficult to destroy and will make it difficult for animal keepers if the sand is already filled with animal waste[:id]Wood Pellet Produk ini berbahan dasar kayu natural atau organik tanpa dicampur dengan bahan kimia sehingga sangat aman bagi hewan peliharaan. Bahkan jika termakan, wood pellet ini akan terbuang melalui feses dalam bentuk yang sudah hancur, tidak dalam bentuk semula. Wood pellet atau pelet kayu berguna sebagai alas\\/substrate pada kandang hewan peliharaan karena menyerap air pipis dan meminimalisir bau kotoran. Beberapa peternak juga menggunakan wood pellet untuk alas hewan peliharaan yang baru lahir \\/ menetas karena kayu yang kami gunakan berbahan natural sehingga hewan akan menyukai kandangnya dan tidak mudah stress. Daya serap tinggi dan harga yang murah \\/ ekonomis mampu menggantikan pasir zeolit yang biasa dipakai untuk alas kandang hewan peliharaan. Pembuangannya pun bisa langsung dibuang ke tanah dan akan hancur dengan tanah. Tidak seperti pasir zeolit yang sulit hancur dan akan menyulitkan pemelihara hewan jika pasir tersebut sudah dipenuhi kotoran hewan.[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#707070\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
