ea77c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Indonesia is a popular location for furniture manufacturing. Consequently a considerable quantitiy of waste is generated by the many companies located within the area.[:id]Indonesia adalah negara produsen furnitur dalam skala besar. Sejumlah besar limbah dihasilkan oleh banyak perusahaan yang berlokasi di Indonesia.[:]\\n\\n[:en]Customary disposal environmentally acceptable and responsible method of waste management could be implemented.\\nWe proceed to explore the potential for the use of this waste and seek an acceptable solution.[:id]Dibutuhkan metode pembuangan limbah dan pengelolaan sampah yang ramah lingkungan dan bertanggung jawab.\\nKami melanjutkan untuk mengeksplorasi potensi penggunaan limbah ini dan menggunakan solusi terbaik.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"32\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"49\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f2460a6\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"marvy_firework_animation_color_multiples\":[{\"color\":\"#f51720\",\"_id\":\"e0d223b\"},{\"color\":\"#fa26a0\",\"_id\":\"b28f5dc\"},{\"color\":\"#f8d210\",\"_id\":\"1e247c9\"},{\"color\":\"#2ff3e0\",\"_id\":\"a359f41\"}],\"marvy_beyblade_animation_color_multiples\":[{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"ac6b442\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"ed2a2dc\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"a1e05bc\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"ab2f81c\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"5ff13ca\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"22c515a\"}],\"structure\":\"20\",\"slider_delay\":\"5000\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-High-Quality-Wood-Pellet.jpg\",\"id\":3665},\"background_size_mobile\":\"cover\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_effect\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_direction\":\"negative\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_speed\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"69c939c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":42.75,\"slider_delay\":\"5000\"},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ac2e026\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":57.25,\"slider_delay\":\"5000\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c28d4e3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]We are one of the best producers of wood pellets, Epal wood pallets, Wood shavings, Sawdust, Wood chips, etc. The company was founded in Indonesia. The main goal is to produce environmentally friendly wood pellets. From the beginning we set ourselves the task of organizing the production, which would produce the highest quality products that complies with all European standards. We mainly focused on ecologically clean regions of Indonesia.<\\/p><p>The raw materials used by non-polluting waste timber and sawmill. When selecting equipment, we are primarily guided by its reliability, performance, and environmental friendliness.<br \\/> [:id]Kami adalah salah satu produsen terbaik untuk wood pellet, Serutan Kayu, Serbuk Gergaji, Serpihan Kayu, dll. Perusahaan kami berdiri di Indonesia. Kami memiliki tujuan utama untuk menghasilkan produk yang ramah lingkungan. Sejak awal kami menetapkan untuk menghasilkan produk dengan kualitas terbaik yang sesuai dengan standar Eropa. Kami berfokus pada wilayah yang bersih secara ekologis di Indonesia.<\\/p><p>Bahan baku yang digunakan oleh kayu limbah dan penggergajian kayu. Dengan perlengkapan optimal, kami mengutamakan kehandalan, kinerja, dan keramahan lingkungan.[:]<\\/p>\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"text_color\":\"#d8d8d8\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"17\",\"right\":\"17\",\"bottom\":\"17\",\"left\":\"17\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"rgba(12,12,12,0.59)\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0234f64\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"21\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"25\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"83d8843\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4a85219\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Indonesia is the highest biomass potential in South East Asia countries so that the chances of developing wood pellet industry is huge.<\\/p><p>Indonesia have many various types of pellets (wood pellet, torrefied wood pellet &amp; charcoal pellet) Biomass decomposition regimes[:id]Indonesia merupakan negara dengan potensi biomassa tertinggi di Asia Tenggara sehingga peluang pengembangan industri wood pellet yang sangat besar.<br \\/>Indonesia memiliki berbagai jenis pelet kayu, pelet kayu torrefied &amp; pelet arang[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#757575\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8223bad\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"68\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3f8dd89\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"687b087\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]WOOD PELLETS FOR CATTLE STALL AND PET LITTER[:id]WOOD PELLET UNTUK KANDANG HEWAN[:]\",\"title_color\":\"#7f7f7f\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"align\":\"center\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-cattle-stall-and-pet-litter\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"2845abf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-Animal-Bedding-and-Litter.jpg\",\"id\":3606},\"image_size\":\"300crop\",\"align\":\"center\",\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-cattle-stall-and-pet-litter\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"7e0582a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"231f137\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]For pets and stable, the animal bedding is a significant part to guarantee the live quality of the animals.\\u00a0Wood pellets for animal bedding have strict quality requirements. Compare it with other animal bedding, wood pellets show a better adsorbing performance which can adsorb the animal excrement, lower the ammonia gas in the stable to keep the stable clean and dry.[:id]Untuk hewan peliharaan dan kandang, tempat tidur hewan merupakan bagian penting untuk menjamin kualitas hidup mereka.\\u00a0Pelet kayu untuk tempat tidur hewan memiliki persyaratan kualitas yang ketat. Dibandingkan dengan bahan lainnya, pelet kayu memiliki daya serap yang lebih baik, mengurangi gas amonia di kandang sehingga menjaga kandang tetap bersih dan kering.[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"58163e4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\"><a style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\