ea77c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Indonesia is a popular location for furniture manufacturing. Consequently a considerable quantitiy of waste is generated by the many companies located within the area.[:id]Indonesia adalah negara produsen furnitur dalam skala besar. Sejumlah besar limbah dihasilkan oleh banyak perusahaan yang berlokasi di Indonesia.[:]\\n\\n[:en]Customary disposal environmentally acceptable and responsible method of waste management could be implemented.\\nWe proceed to explore the potential for the use of this waste and seek an acceptable solution.[:id]Dibutuhkan metode pembuangan limbah dan pengelolaan sampah yang ramah lingkungan dan bertanggung jawab.\\nKami melanjutkan untuk mengeksplorasi potensi penggunaan limbah ini dan menggunakan solusi terbaik.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"32\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"49\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f2460a6\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"marvy_firework_animation_color_multiples\":[{\"color\":\"#f51720\",\"_id\":\"e0d223b\"},{\"color\":\"#fa26a0\",\"_id\":\"b28f5dc\"},{\"color\":\"#f8d210\",\"_id\":\"1e247c9\"},{\"color\":\"#2ff3e0\",\"_id\":\"a359f41\"}],\"marvy_beyblade_animation_color_multiples\":[{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"ac6b442\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"ed2a2dc\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"a1e05bc\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"ab2f81c\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"5ff13ca\"},{\"color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"_id\":\"22c515a\"}],\"structure\":\"20\",\"slider_delay\":\"5000\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-High-Quality-Wood-Pellet.jpg\",\"id\":3665},\"background_size_mobile\":\"cover\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_effect\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_direction\":\"negative\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_speed\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"69c939c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":42.75,\"slider_delay\":\"5000\"},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ac2e026\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":57.25,\"slider_delay\":\"5000\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c28d4e3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]We are one of the best producers of wood pellets, Epal wood pallets, Wood shavings, Sawdust, Wood chips, etc. The company was founded in Indonesia. The main goal is to produce environmentally friendly wood pellets. From the beginning we set ourselves the task of organizing the production, which would produce the highest quality products that complies with all European standards. We mainly focused on ecologically clean regions of Indonesia.<\\/p><p>The raw materials used by non-polluting waste timber and sawmill. When selecting equipment, we are primarily guided by its reliability, performance, and environmental friendliness.<br \\/> [:id]Kami adalah salah satu produsen terbaik untuk wood pellet, Serutan Kayu, Serbuk Gergaji, Serpihan Kayu, dll. Perusahaan kami berdiri di Indonesia. Kami memiliki tujuan utama untuk menghasilkan produk yang ramah lingkungan. Sejak awal kami menetapkan untuk menghasilkan produk dengan kualitas terbaik yang sesuai dengan standar Eropa. Kami berfokus pada wilayah yang bersih secara ekologis di Indonesia.<\\/p><p>Bahan baku yang digunakan oleh kayu limbah dan penggergajian kayu. Dengan perlengkapan optimal, kami mengutamakan kehandalan, kinerja, dan keramahan lingkungan.[:]<\\/p>\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"text_color\":\"#d8d8d8\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"17\",\"right\":\"17\",\"bottom\":\"17\",\"left\":\"17\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"rgba(12,12,12,0.59)\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0234f64\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"21\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"25\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"83d8843\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4a85219\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Indonesia is the highest biomass potential in South East Asia countries so that the chances of developing wood pellet industry is huge.<\\/p><p>Indonesia have many various types of pellets (wood pellet, torrefied wood pellet &amp; charcoal pellet) Biomass decomposition regimes[:id]Indonesia merupakan negara dengan potensi biomassa tertinggi di Asia Tenggara sehingga peluang pengembangan industri wood pellet yang sangat besar.<br \\/>Indonesia memiliki berbagai jenis pelet kayu, pelet kayu torrefied &amp; pelet arang[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#757575\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8223bad\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"68\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3f8dd89\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"687b087\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]WOOD PELLETS FOR CATTLE STALL AND PET LITTER[:id]WOOD PELLET UNTUK KANDANG HEWAN[:]\",\"title_color\":\"#7f7f7f\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"align\":\"center\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-cattle-stall-and-pet-litter\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"2845abf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-Animal-Bedding-and-Litter.jpg\",\"id\":3606},\"image_size\":\"300crop\",\"align\":\"center\",\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-cattle-stall-and-pet-litter\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"7e0582a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"231f137\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]For pets and stable, the animal bedding is a significant part to guarantee the live quality of the animals.\\u00a0Wood pellets for animal bedding have strict quality requirements. Compare it with other animal bedding, wood pellets show a better adsorbing performance which can adsorb the animal excrement, lower the ammonia gas in the stable to keep the stable clean and dry.[:id]Untuk hewan peliharaan dan kandang, tempat tidur hewan merupakan bagian penting untuk menjamin kualitas hidup mereka.\\u00a0Pelet kayu untuk tempat tidur hewan memiliki persyaratan kualitas yang ketat. Dibandingkan dengan bahan lainnya, pelet kayu memiliki daya serap yang lebih baik, mengurangi gas amonia di kandang sehingga menjaga kandang tetap bersih dan kering.[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"58163e4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\"><a style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-cattle-stall-and-pet-litter\\\">[:en]More Info[:id]Info Selengkapnya[:]<\\/a><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"text_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"bold\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"11\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"8\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"#c6601b\",\"_box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"81fb1dd\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"71\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c810a8e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e43c174\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]WOOD PELLETS FOR HEATING ENERGY GENERATION[:id]WOOD PELLET UNTUK SUMBER ENERGI[:]\",\"title_color\":\"#7f7f7f\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"align\":\"center\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-heating-energy-generation\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"1885a51\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-burning.jpg\",\"id\":3609},\"image_size\":\"300crop\",\"align\":\"center\",\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-heating-energy-generation\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"85a9e93\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ea9c2f6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Nowadays, the environmental problem catches everyone\\u2019s eyes. The traditional way to generate heating energy (burning fossil fuel such as coal) has been criticized by the people. In order to lower the carbon emission, the central heating systems have no other ways but finding a substitute that is environmentally friendly.\\n\\nAnd, wood pellets, obviously, is a perfect choice. Wood pellets not only burn so efficiently but also environmentally - friendly. Wood pellets are made from wood wastes and can be recycled. And wood pellets release just much less amount of carbon dioxide emission than any other type of traditional fuel.[:id]\\nSaat ini, masalah lingkungan menjadi perhatian semua pihak. Cara tradisional untuk menghasilkan energi pemanas (pembakaran bahan bakar fosil seperti batu bara) banyak dikritik masyarakat. Untuk menurunkan emisi karbon membutuhkan pengganti yang ramah lingkungan.\\n\\nPelet kayu merupakan pilihan terbaik. Pelet kayu membakar dengan sangat efisien dan ramah lingkungan. Pelet kayu terbuat dari limbah kayu dan dapat didaur ulang, melepaskan jumlah emisi karbon dioksida yang jauh lebih sedikit daripada jenis bahan bakar tradisional lainnya.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"7cb93e3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<span style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\"><a style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]wood-pellet-for-heating-energy-generation\\\">[:en]More Info[:id]Info Selengkapnya[:]<\\/a><\\/span>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"text_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"bold\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"11\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"8\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"#c6601b\",\"_box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"2975bb3\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"71\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7fbc24b\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3a15eed\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]SAW DUST[:id]SERBUK GERGAJI[:]\",\"title_color\":\"#7f7f7f\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"align\":\"center\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]saw-dust\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"4a77ae1\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Saw-Dust.jpg\",\"id\":3732},\"image_size\":\"300crop\",\"align\":\"center\",\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]saw-dust\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"13bfa8c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9125479\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]We supply Sawdust powder that is waste from furniture woodworking operation. Our sawdust powder is produced from mahogany wood, teak wood, oak wood, albasia wood, an rubber tree wood. The sawdust powder can be used as animal bedding, garden mulch, partikel board material or as burning material to replace the coal that is used in the industries.[:id]Kami menyediakan serbuk gergaji yang merupakan limbah dari pengerjaan kayu furnitur. Serbuk gergaji kami diproduksi dari kayu mahoni, kayu jati, kayu oak, kayu albasia, kayu pohon karet. Serbuk serbuk gergaji dapat digunakan sebagai alas hewan, kebun, bahan papan partikel atau sebagai bahan bakar untuk menggantikan batubara yang digunakan dalam industri.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"ce42b49\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<span style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\"><a style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/[:id]id\\/[:]saw-dust\\\">[:en]More Info[:id]Info Selengkapnya[:]<\\/a><\\/span>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"text_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"bold\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"11\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"8\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"#c6601b\",\"_box_shadow_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"7700d95\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"height\":\"min-height\",\"custom_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":384,\"sizes\":[]},\"custom_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":392,\"sizes\":[]},\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Eco-Friendly-Indonesia-Wood-Pellet.jpeg\",\"id\":3668},\"background_position\":\"center center\",\"background_position_mobile\":\"center center\",\"background_xpos_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":113,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_ypos_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"vh\",\"size\":\"\",\"sizes\":[]},\"background_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_repeat_mobile\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_size\":\"contain\",\"background_size_mobile\":\"cover\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"ye