e_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_effect\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_direction\":\"negative\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_speed\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10,\"sizes\":[]},\"custom_height_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":450,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_position_tablet\":\"center center\",\"background_position_mobile\":\"center center\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7da6629\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":53.04,\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"rgba(12,12,12,0.35)\",\"slider_delay\":\"5000\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation\":\"fadeInUp\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation_duration\":\"fast\",\"margin_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":false},\"animation\":\"fadeInUp\",\"animation_duration\":\"fast\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4d990a3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]High Quality Wood Pellet[:id]Wood Pellet Kualitas Terbaik[:]\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"title_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation\":\"fadeInRight\",\"_animation\":\"fadeInUp\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"a38e8d2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Premium provider of wood pellets directly to your place through our manufacturing sources[:id]Penyedia wood pellet premium dikirim langsung dari pabrik ke tempat Anda[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#f2f2f2\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_line_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.4,\"sizes\":[]},\"pafe_absolute_positioning_top\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_right\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_bottom\":\"auto\",\"pafe_absolute_positioning_left\":\"auto\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation\":\"fadeInRight\",\"pafe_slider_builder_animation_duration\":\"slow\",\"_animation\":\"fadeInUp\",\"animation_duration\":\"slow\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9fa48ce\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":46.96,\"slider_delay\":\"5000\"},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a12a26a\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"67e6487\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ebeb35d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]How Biomass Wood Pellets Made?[:id]Pembuatan Pelet Kayu Biomass[:]\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#828282\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":22,\"sizes\":[]},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"2c68e94\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]To create wood pellets, producers remove moisture from incoming wood fibre, grind the fibre into dust, and compress the dust into small cylinders\\u2014pellets\\u2014typically with a 6 or 8 mm diameter, and a length of up to 40 mm. Heat is applied in this process which causes lignin\\u2014a natural polymer found in wood\\u2014to act as a glue to hold the compressed particles together. The result is a dry, highly compressed and high energy-value product that can be easily handled and transported efficiently over very long distances.[:id]Untuk membuat pelet kayu, produsen menghilangkan kelembapan dari serat kayu yang masuk, menggiling serat menjadi debu, dan memampatkan debu menjadi silinder kecil\\u2014pelet\\u2014biasanya dengan diameter 6 atau 8 mm, dan panjang hingga 40 mm. Panas diterapkan dalam proses ini yang menyebabkan lignin\\u2014polimer alami yang ditemukan di kayu\\u2014bertindak sebagai lem untuk menyatukan partikel yang terkompresi. Hasilnya adalah produk kering, terkompresi tinggi, dan bernilai energi tinggi yang dapat dengan mudah ditangani dan diangkut secara efisien dalam jarak yang sangat jauh.[:]\",\"text_color\":\"#636363\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c991685\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"height\":\"min-height\",\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Biomass-Wood-Pellet.jpg\",\"id\":3747},\"background_position\":\"center center\",\"background_position_mobile\":\"bottom center\",\"background_size\":\"cover\",\"background_size_mobile\":\"cover\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_effect\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_direction\":\"negative\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_speed\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8279e4c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":54.171},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"72de736\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Wood pellets are biofuels made from compressed wood fibre.\\nWood pellets are made primarily from the residuals left over from the sawmilling process when logs are converted into lumber and other high-value wood products. Increasingly, harvesting residuals in the forest and low-quality logs once left as waste are also a source of raw material for wood pellets. By making wood pellets from fibre that was once burned or left behind, the wood pellet sector is reducing waste and turning that debris into valuable, low carbon biofuel.[:id]Pelet kayu adalah biofuel yang terbuat dari serat kayu terkompresi.\\nPelet kayu dibuat terutama dari residu yang tersisa dari proses penggergajian kayu ketika kayu bulat diubah menjadi kayu dan produk kayu bernilai tinggi lainnya. Semakin banyak, sisa panen di hutan dan kayu bulat berkualitas rendah yang dulu ditinggalkan sebagai limbah juga menjadi sumber bahan baku pelet kayu. Dengan membuat pelet kayu dari serat yang pernah dibakar atau ditinggalkan, sektor pelet kayu mengurangi limbah dan mengubah puing-puing itu menjadi biofuel rendah karbon yang berharga.[:]\\n\",\"text_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_line_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.1,\"sizes\":[]},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"5\",\"right\":\"6\",\"bottom\":\"5\",\"left\":\"5\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.48)\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"65a7678\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":45.829},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0ad3c8b\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"722bc24\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c286b10\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"carousel\":[{\"id\":3747,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Biomass-Wood-Pellet.jpg\"},{\"id\":3754,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Biomass-Wood-Pellets.jpeg\"},{\"id\":3755,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Pile-Of-Burning-Beech-Pellets.jpg\"},{\"id\":3668,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Eco-Friendly-Indonesia-Wood-Pellet.jpeg\"},{\"id\":3757,\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-wood-pellets-for-biomass-boilers.jpg\"}],\"thumbnail_size\":\"300crop\",\"slides_to_show\":\"3\",\"slides_to_show_mobile\":\"2\",\"slides_to_scroll_mobile\":\"1\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-carousel\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c7c65fe\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"01be02a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a8b9142\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"text\":\"Divider\",\"color\":\"#d1d1d1\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"divider\"},{\"id\":\"7b113af\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"[:en]An efficient sustainable source of energy[:id]Sumber energi berkelanjutan yang efisien[:]\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#999999\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":20,\"sizes\":[]},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"41\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"4087828\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Wood pellets are used in both domestic and industrial applications. Many people in colder climates worldwide use wood pellet boilers or stoves to heat their homes. Today\\u2019s modern boilers are so well automated that they need no human operator or maintenance beyond loading a winter season worth of pellets, pressing a button to start the system and removing the ash six months later. Stoves are more common in North America. Pellets are simply fed by hand into the stove\\u2019s hopper and continuously burned to create an efficient, even heat source. Particulate emissions from modern pellet heating equipment are similar, and in some cases lower, than conventional fossil fuel boilers and furnaces. For industrial electricity generation, wood pellets are used as a low-carbon alternative in place of coal. Pellets are ground back to dust, the dust is combined with air, and the resulting mixture is fed continuously to a flame which creates steam to generate electricity.Wood pellets are used in both domestic and industrial applications. Many people in colder climates worldwide use wood pellet boil