(1661, 3728, '_madxartwork_data', '[{\"id\":\"6f60435\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b7ea559\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7cc58b8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Add Your Heading Text Here\",\"title_color\":\"#969696\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":28,\"sizes\":[]},\"__dynamic__\":{\"title\":\"[madxartwork-tag id=\\\"1393853\\\" name=\\\"post-title\\\" settings=\\\"%7B%7D\\\"]\",\"link\":\"[madxartwork-tag id=\\\"e33ff8b\\\" name=\\\"post-url\\\" settings=\\\"%7B%7D\\\"]\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"102e5dc\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"height\":\"min-height\",\"custom_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":439,\"sizes\":[]},\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Saw-Dust.jpg\",\"id\":3732},\"background_size\":\"cover\",\"background_motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_effect\":\"yes\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_direction\":\"negative\",\"background_motion_fx_translateY_speed\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bac3986\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"4f8a121\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null,\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.44)\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ea763e7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]We supply Sawdust powder that is waste from furniture woodworking operation. Our sawdust powder is produced from mahogany wood, teak wood, oak wood, albasia wood, an rubber tree wood. The sawdust powder can be used as animal bedding, garden mulch, partikel board material or as burning material to replace the coal that is used in the industries.[:id]Kami menyediakan serbuk gergaji yang merupakan limbah dari pengerjaan kayu furnitur. Serbuk gergaji kami diproduksi dari kayu mahoni, kayu jati, kayu oak, kayu albasia, kayu pohon karet. Serbuk serbuk gergaji dapat digunakan sebagai alas hewan, kebun, bahan papan partikel atau sebagai bahan bakar untuk menggantikan batubara yang digunakan dalam industri.[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#ffffff\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"cd9ca60\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7b190bb\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"304f254\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>[:en]Sawdust, a relatively abundant and inexpensive material is currently being investigated as an adsorbent to remove contaminants from water. Chemical substances including dyes, oil, toxic salts and heavy metals can be removed very effectively with the organic material.<br \\/>Wood sawdust is much beneficial to cultivation and animal bedding. Since for cultivation, wood sawdust adds more nutrients to dry and hard soil after a long period of planting. Sawdust also provides your animal with a clean and comfortable place to live.[:id]Serbuk gergaji, bahan yang relatif melimpah dan murah berfungsi sebagai adsorben untuk menghilangkan kontaminan dari air. Zat kimia termasuk pewarna, minyak, garam beracun dan logam berat dapat dihilangkan dengan sangat efektif dengan bahan organik ini.<br \\/>Serbuk gergaji kayu sangat bermanfaat untuk budidaya dan tempat tidur hewan. Karena untuk budidaya, serbuk gergaji kayu menambahkan lebih banyak nutrisi ke tanah yang kering dan keras setelah masa tanam yang lama. Serbuk gergaji juga memberi hewan Anda tempat yang bersih dan nyaman untuk hidup.[:]<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#7c7c7c\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
