(1717, 3769, '_madxartwork_data', '[{\"id\":\"63a1e3e\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6bf09c0\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8c43237\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Add Your Heading Text Here\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#aaaaaa\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":23,\"sizes\":[]},\"__dynamic__\":{\"title\":\"[madxartwork-tag id=\\\"67d897a\\\" name=\\\"post-title\\\" settings=\\\"%7B%7D\\\"]\",\"link\":\"[madxartwork-tag id=\\\"545ae63\\\" name=\\\"post-url\\\" settings=\\\"%7B%7D\\\"]\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"17205c4\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4c12f0e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4f0d6a2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/livestock-using-wood-pellets.jpg\",\"id\":3709}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"c9985ee\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"344531f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":31.256},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5163eea\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/smdiputra.co.id\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/10\\/Indonesia-Albasia-Wood.jpg\",\"id\":3705},\"image_size\":\"medium_large\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8ea1d56\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":68.744},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7211f6c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"[:en]Currently Falcataria moluccana \\/ Albasia wood became one of the raw materials in the manufactured of wood pellets, because F. moluccana has a fast growing properties. However F. moluccana pellets have a high ash content, and high S and N content, with low calorific value which could not meet requirement of EnPlus standard for pellet. To improve its properties, pellets were manufactured using mixtures of F. moluccana particles to coconut shell particles, and the properties were investigated. The objectives of this study were to determine effect of the combination material of F. moluccana with coconut shell on different particle size and different compressive force. A material was from F. moluccana sawdust waste and coconut shell waste (Cocos nucifera L.). [:id]Kayu sengon menjadi salah satu bahan baku dalam pembuatan pelet kayu karena memiliki sifat yang cepat tumbuh. Akan tetapi pelet kayu sengon memiliki kadar abu, kadar sulfur dan nitrogen yang tinggi serta nilai kalor yang rendah sehingga belum dapat memenuhi spesifikasi standar pelet kayu (EnPlus). Untuk meningkatkan sifat bahan bakar pelet kayu maka dilakukan pencampuran bahan dengan serbuk tempurung kelapa. Diketahui tempurung kelapa memiliki nilai kalor yang tinggi, dan kadar abu, sulfur dan nitrogen yang rendah. Penelitian ini bertujuan untuk mengetahui pengaruh kombinasi bahan sengon dengan tempurung kelapa pada ukuran partikel dan tekanan kempa yang berbeda. Penelitian ini menggunakan bahan dari limbah serbuk gergaji sengon (Falcataria moluccana (Miq.)) dan limbah tempurung kelapa (Cocos nucifera). [:]\",\"text_color\":\"#7f7f7f\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"9f92353\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"height\":\"min-height\",\"custom_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":450,\"sizes\":[]},\"custom_height_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":450,\"sizes\":[]},\"marvy_firework_animation_color_multiples\":[{\"color\":\"#f51720\",\"_id\":\"d534a3a\"},{\"color\":\"#fa26a0\",\"_id\":\"476c0fa\"},{\"color\":\"#f8d210\",\"_id\":\"7be2fbd\"},{\"color\":\"#2ff3e0\",\"_id\":\"fe