 menjamin kualitas hidup hewan[:]\n		</section>\n										<img width=\"571\" height=\"401\" src=\"https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/about.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/about.jpg 571w, https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/about-300x211.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" />											\n		<p>[:en]We are one of the best producers of wood pellets, Epal wood pallets, Wood shavings, Sawdust, Wood chips, etc. The company was founded in Indonesia. The main goal is to produce environmentally friendly wood pellets. From the beginning we set ourselves the task of organizing the production, which would produce the highest quality products that complies with all European standards. We mainly focused on ecologically clean regions of Indonesia.</p><p>The raw materials used by non-polluting waste timber and sawmill. When selecting equipment, we are primarily guided by its reliability, performance, and environmental friendliness.<br /> [:id]Kami adalah salah satu produsen terbaik untuk wood pellet, Serutan Kayu, Serbuk Gergaji, Serpihan Kayu, dll. Perusahaan kami berdiri di Indonesia. Kami memiliki tujuan utama untuk menghasilkan produk yang ramah lingkungan. Sejak awal kami menetapkan untuk menghasilkan produk dengan kualitas terbaik yang sesuai dengan standar Eropa. Kami berfokus pada wilayah yang bersih secara ekologis di Indonesia.</p><p>Bahan baku yang digunakan oleh kayu limbah dan penggergajian kayu. Dengan perlengkapan optimal, kami mengutamakan kehandalan, kinerja, dan keramahan lingkungan.[:]</p>		\n			<h2>WOOD PELLETS FOR ANIMAL BEDDING AND PET LITTER</h2>		\n										<img width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-Animal-Bedding-and-Litter-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-Animal-Bedding-and-Litter-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-Animal-Bedding-and-Litter-225x300.jpg 225w, https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-Animal-Bedding-and-Litter.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" />											\n		For pets and stable, the animal bedding is a significant part to guarantee the live quality of the animals.\nWood pellets for animal bedding have strict quality requirements. Compare it with other animal bedding, wood pellets show a better adsorbing performance which can adsorb the animal excrement, lower the ammonia gas in the stable to keep the stable clean and dry.		\n			<h2>WOOD PELLETS FOR HEATING ENERGY GENERATION</h2>		\n										<img width=\"768\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-burning-768x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-burning-768x576.jpg 768w, https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-burning-300x225.jpg 300w, https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-burning-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://smdiputra.co.id/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Indonesia-Wood-Pellet-for-burning.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" />											\n		<p>Nowadays, the environmental problem catches everyone’s eyes. The traditional way to generate heating energy (burning fossil fuel such as coal) has been criticized by the people. In order to lower the carbon emission, the central heating systems have no other ways but finding a substitute that is environmentally friendly.</p><p>And, wood pellets, obviously, is a perfect choice. Wood pellets not only burn so efficiently but also environmentally - friendly. Wood pellets are made from wood wastes and can be recycled. And wood pellets release just much less amount of carbon dioxide emission than any other type of traditional fuel.</p>', '[:en]Home[:id